Meet GPL family license standards

- Add lice:program-name custom variable to replace `this program`
string in the license notices

- Add `This file is part of lice:program-name.` line in the license
notices

- Add lice:program-description custom variable to add the description
line before copyright notice

Allow setting copyright holder in .dir-locals.el

Allow setting copyright holder in .dir-locals.el

The default is still (user-full-name). But now it can be customized, and
more importantly it can be overridden in .dir-locals.el.
This might be useful if you are working in a project where you want to
assign copyright to a project or team or such.
